N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 733.12 - Records of services performed by associated companies

State Regulations

Each public utility or municipality to which the
regulations in this Part apply shall assure the availability of records of
services performed by associated companies for the periods indicated in this

Part, as are necessary, to support the cost of services rendered to it by an
associated company. Notes
